column2: ggplot(df1[df1$variable == type,],aes(x=name,y=value)) + geom_bar(stat="identity", fill = "dodgerblue") + xlab("Filter Activation Combination") + ylab(type) + ggtitle(paste("Average", type)) + theme_bw() + theme(panel.border = element_blank(), panel.grid.major = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(), axis.ticks.x=element_blank(), axis.ticks.y=element_blank(), plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5), axis.line = element_line(colour = "black"))
